    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年6月30日-2025年7月4日）",
    "followRuleId": "1257180121148821504",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span> </span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1257185687753592832&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">《京东开放平台开票规则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>核心内容：</strong>规定京东给商家开具发票、以及商家给京东开具发票的相关行为规范。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>关联规则：</strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1257213261586239488&amp;btype=12\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">《京东开放平台个人/个体开店管理规则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1256844990940844032\">《京东开放平台商家套利细则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>核心内容：</strong>调整商家套利违规场景定义及处理措施。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>关联规则：</strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1256844990940844032&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1257155162670239744\">《京东开放平台超级味觉品质认证标准》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>核心内容：</strong>明确<strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-weight: normal;\">京东超级味觉的定义、</span></strong>认证标准及流程。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1257221375291166720\">《2025年7月京东开放平台个人/个体-厨房小电品类销售激励政策》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>核心内容：</strong>个人/个体店主营为家用电器&gt;厨房小电类目指定品牌店铺达成GMV目标并满足环比增长要求，可享受对应GMV阶梯折扣。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1257320186810339328\">《京东开放平台店铺命名规则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>核心内容：</strong>新增店铺名称及logo中不得使用京东已注册或其他可能给消费者造成混淆或误解的相关名称的条款。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1257320186810339328\">《京东开放平台店铺logo管理规则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>核心内容：</strong>新增店铺名称及logo中不得使用京东已注册或其他可能给消费者造成混淆或误解的相关名称的条款。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则生效】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\">《<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1255789833545191424\">京东开放平台大时尚品类新商激励政策（2025.7.1-2025.9.30）》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2025</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年Q3入驻的京东开放平台时尚相关类目的商家，当GMV达到相关要求，将可获发专项激励金额，专项激励金用于广告投放。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #f8f8f9;\">2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #f8f8f9;\">、【修订】</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1255761115896483840\">《京东开放平台商家保证金管理规则》</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #f8f8f9;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">因保证金GMV阈值合并，保证金规则举例部分，按照最新收费挡位同步调整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1254622809850777600&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台非全新商品管理规则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">新增非全新商品管理要求，包括非全新商品商品信息要求、违规处理措施等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1255847210776662016\">《京东开放平台店铺综合体验分规则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">五星店铺认证范围调整为在京东开放平台入驻开店的旗舰店、专卖店、专营店、卖场店店铺。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1255044522015068160&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台商品质量不合格细则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">调整质量违规场景定义②增加综合认定质量问题定义及对应处理措施③删除质量客诉场景④调整附则等相关表述。</span></p>",
